## WSL2

### Проверка статуса
```powershell
wsl -l -v
```

### Установка QEMU
```powershell
wsl -d Debian -- bash -c "echo 'nameserver 8.8.8.8' | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf && sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install -y qemu-system-x86 qemu-utils cloud-image-utils unzip"
```

### Установка Packer в WSL2
```powershell
wsl -d Debian -- bash -c "wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/packer/1.11.2/packer_1.11.2_linux_amd64.zip && unzip packer_1.11.2_linux_amd64.zip && sudo mv packer /usr/local/bin/ && rm packer_1.11.2_linux_amd64.zip"
```
